Package: text2data
Title: Convert plain text to datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joe", "Ornstein", , "jornstein@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5704-2098"))
Description: The text2data package allows R users to submit prompts to OpenAI's GPT-3 API. Includes handy functions for formatting prompts, classifying texts according to user-defined instructions, and converting plain text into structured datasets.
